{"tid":2280001,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GFriend Yerin出道後多次「進化」 疑發福變臉傳整容","createTime":"2020-11-10T07:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T13:56:45.000Z","uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"710353614a0b7ccafa66b7f23ef2067f154ea3b9","tid":2280001,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LGLXH7Gi8hgC00gOkHG5lO9qfmg=/538x302/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MWX7DLI3KJEGLDQBJVMMIXTZFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLGLXH7Gi8hgC00gOkHG5lO9qfmg%3D%2F538x302%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMWX7DLI3KJEGLDQBJVMMIXTZFU.jpg&h=b349a291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國女團GFriend今日於首爾舉行showcase，宣傳新碟《回:Walpurgis Night》，一眾成員均以新look示人，當中24歲的Yerin疑似變臉而引起熱議。<br />\n今日Yerin以粉紅色的髮色示人，穿上小背心的她於台上風騷擺甫士，不過就被發現腰間現贅肉，加上臉圓圓，似乎發福不少。除了身形引關注外，Yerin再次「進化」的樣貌亦引起熱議。Yerin於2015年出道時仍有baby fat、鼻樑亦不算高挺，不過就有甜美笑容搭夠，憑青春可愛的樣子冧fans。但近年Yerin逐漸現尖下巴及筆直的鼻樑，加上雙眼變大而且嘴唇變厚，而今日她現身時，就因為臉圓圓，令外界猜測她是否打了蘋果肌。不過有fans力撐偶像，認為Yerin只是改變了化妝風格，加上輕微發福而望落稍為不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3a8urF997jUjEbQq-XfdZPe5q0k=/538x807/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZEJMB6DQ3BDDJIBSWQQNNSQRNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3a8urF997jUjEbQq-XfdZPe5q0k%3D%2F538x807%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZEJMB6DQ3BDDJIBSWQQNNSQRNU.jpg&h=20e569a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fiI9DAlohFYACtDe_62extb7E7s=/538x798/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6U2KFWJ5WNDAXMMNXDKPZZY3CI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ap